This is a small utility to download the open course videos on Coursera in batch.

Step 1:
Enroll into a class.

Step 2:
Save the page with video watching as an html file called source.html.

Step 3:
Export the cookie for Coursera using Chrome or Firefox plugins and name it as cookies.txt.

Step 4:
Put all these things and the code under the same folder.

Step 5:
Then run perl downloader.pl and wait for the download to complete!